{"tid":1164412,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"華為高管用蘋果，任正非回應：我家人也用iPhone，你怎麼看？","createTime":"2019-05-21T05:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T13:41:27.000Z","uid":109923,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8902dbd2e802dbbe69013699b13271a4b51b168f","tid":1164412,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T05:16:36.000Z","msg":"近日，有外媒報導稱，華為CFO孟晚舟的隨身物品中攜帶了四種電子設備，其中只有一款是華為的產品，為華為Mate20保時捷版，而另外三種全部都是蘋果的產品，其中有蘋果的手機、筆記本以及平板。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G8H0aGK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG8H0aGK.png&h=bf098a9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（推特截圖）<br />\n<br />\n任正非在深圳接受加拿大媒體採訪時表示，他個人是非常敬佩喬布斯的，因為他&ldquo;是改變了人類社會的偉人&rdquo;，儘管他自己堅持使用華為產品，但他的家人會使用蘋果手機。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JS0H8tr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJS0H8tr.png&h=4f51c245&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（CTV News報導截圖）<br />\n<br />\n對此，有人認為任正非一番話體現出了中國企業家尊重、正視競爭對手的大度，有人認為華為這表明華為對自己的產品沒有信心，也有網友表示華為高管私底下使用別家的產品也是個人自由，畢竟不是工作時間。<br />\n<br />\n特別聲明：本文為網易自媒體平台&ldquo;網易號&rdquo;作者上傳並發布，僅代表該作者觀點。網易僅提供信息發布平台。<br />\n<br />\n(責任編輯：李黎霞_NBJ10747)"},{"pid":"351f0f331de0826a19b0ae280d562219b6304877","tid":1164412,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T05:22:14.000Z","msg":"向太都&rdquo;叫人&rdquo;愛國用屎為<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K2jFaJG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK2jFaJG.png&h=ebde5258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2350000/2354805/20190521_heung_02_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2350000%2F2354805%2F20190521_heung_02_600.jpg&h=43301c00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c13c838dabbf7cd30f49f6fd050fcb5984e923b6","tid":1164412,"uid":109383,"like":11,"dislike":5,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"